\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><a href=\"#main-content\" class=\"skip-nav\">Skip to main content</a><main id=\"main-content\" class=\"min-h-screen bg-grid px-4 py-5 text-slate-100 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><header class=\"mb-8 flex flex-col gap-5 border-b border-white/10 pb-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"brand-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M5 14c5 0 9-3 12-8 1 7-2 12-8 13-2 .3-4-2-4-5Z\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path><path d=\"M7 17c2-3 5-5 9-7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></path></svg></span><div><p class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white\">CarbonPulse</p><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Small actions. Measurable impact.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"status-pill\"><span class=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-300\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>Data stays on this device</span></div></header><section class=\"mb-7 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[1.35fr_.65fr]\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">Your personal dashboard</p><h1 class=\"mt-2 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl\">See the impact of your day, then make tomorrow lighter.</h1><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-400\">Track transport, food, and home energy. Get a clear footprint estimate and one practical next action.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 self-end\"><div class=\"mini-stat\"><span>Today&#x27;s score</span><strong>--</strong><small>out of 100</small></div><div class=\"mini-stat\"><span>Carbon saved</span><strong>0.0</strong><small>kg this week</small></div><div class=\"mini-stat\"><span>Eco points</span><strong>0</strong><small>all time</small></div></div></section><div class=\"sr-only\" aria-live=\"polite\" role=\"status\"></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-12\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-5\"><section class=\"panel panel-accent h-full p-5 sm:p-6\" aria-labelledby=\"log-heading\"><div class=\"mb-5\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">Daily check-in</p><h2 id=\"log-heading\" class=\"mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-white\">Log today&#x27;s activity</h2><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Add one snapshot. CarbonPulse estimates the impact and updates your plan instantly.</p></div><form class=\"space-y-4\" noValidate=\"\"><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><label class=\"field-label\" for=\"transport-mode\">Transport<select id=\"transport-mode\" class=\"field-control\"><option value=\"walk\" selected=\"\">Walking</option><option value=\"cycle\">Cycling</option><option value=\"bus\">Bus</option><option value=\"train\">Train / Metro</option><option value=\"bike\">Motorbike</option><option value=\"car\">Car</option></select></label><label class=\"field-label\" for=\"distance-km\">Distance travelled<span class=\"field-with-unit\"><input id=\"distance-km\" type=\"number\" class=\"field-control pr-12\" required=\"\" min=\"0\" max=\"1000\" step=\"0.1\" placeholder=\"12\" aria-describedby=\"distance-hint\" value=\"\"/><span aria-hidden=\"true\">km</span></span><span id=\"distance-hint\" class=\"sr-only\">Enter distance in kilometres, 0 to 1000</span></label></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><label class=\"field-label\" for=\"diet-type\">Food pattern<select id=\"diet-type\" class=\"field-control\"><option value=\"vegan\">Plant-based</option><option value=\"vegetarian\">Vegetarian</option><option value=\"mixed\" selected=\"\">Mixed diet</option><option value=\"high_meat\">High-meat diet</option></select></label><label class=\"field-label\" for=\"home-energy\">Home electricity<span class=\"field-with-unit\"><input id=\"home-energy\" type=\"number\" class=\"field-control pr-14\" required=\"\" min=\"0\" max=\"500\" step=\"0.1\" placeholder=\"4.5\" aria-describedby=\"energy-hint\" value=\"\"/><span aria-hidden=\"true\">kWh</span></span><span id=\"energy-hint\" class=\"sr-only\">Enter electricity usage in kilowatt-hours, 0 to 500</span></label></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"primary-button w-full\">Calculate my footprint<svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path></svg></button><p class=\"min-h-5 text-center text-xs text-emerald-300\" role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\"></p></form></section></div><section class=\"panel p-5 sm:p-6 lg:col-span-7\" aria-labelledby=\"snapshot-heading\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-start justify-between gap-4\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">Latest snapshot</p><h2 id=\"snapshot-heading\" class=\"mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-white\">Your footprint breakdown</h2></div></div><div class=\"empty-state min-h-52\"><span class=\"empty-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">0</span><p>Your transport, food, and energy breakdown will appear here.</p></div></section><section class=\"panel p-5 sm:p-6 lg:col-span-7\" aria-labelledby=\"trend-heading\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex items-start justify-between\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">Track progress</p><h2 id=\"trend-heading\" class=\"mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">Seven-day footprint trend</h2></div><span class=\"text-right\"><strong class=\"block text-xl font-semibold text-white\">0.0 kg</strong><small class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">logged this week</small></span></div><div class=\"empty-state\"><span class=\"empty-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><p>Log your first day to begin a seven-day trend.</p></div></section><section class=\"panel insight-panel p-5 sm:p-6 lg:col-span-5\" aria-labelledby=\"insight-heading\"><div class=\"flex h-full flex-col\"><p class=\"eyebrow\">Personalized next step</p><h2 id=\"insight-heading\" class=\"mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white\">Your first insight is one log away</h2><p class=\"mt-3 flex-1 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300\">Add transport, food, and electricity data to get a p